Term-Screen-Uni version 0.02
============================

Unified Term::Screen module (works the same on termcap systems and on Win32)


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Term::Screen::Win32 (version 0.01) on Win32 platform
  Term::Screen on other platforms
  Carp


